---
import { LINKS } from "../config/links";
---
<div class="project-preview">
  <div class="preview-entry active" id="1">
    <p>
      A visual mod published for the game Deep Rock Glactic, replacing the default class icons with fresh stylized vector art.
      Art done by BigStwongCreativeMan, first posted in the community subreddit which garnered some attention. 
      I spontaneously contacted and collaborated with CreativeMan to help them implement their art in game. 
      I helped with modding, quality assurance, and presentation.
    </p>
    <a class="drgmod-btn" href={LINKS.projects.drgmod} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mod.io Mod Page</a>
  </div>
  <div class="preview-entry" id="2">
    <p>Preview 1</p>
  </div>
  <div class="preview-entry" id="3">
    <p>Preview 1</p>
  </div>
  <div class="preview-entry" id="4">
  <p>Urban entropy on the streets of Tokyo. Faded graffitis, worn down stickers, alleyways that hasn't kept with the times.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="preview-entry" id="5">
    <p>
       
      <br> Libraries used are: FontAwesome for icons, Matter.js for 2D Physics, Vanta.js for animated background, and gsap for animation and feel. 
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="preview-entry" id="6">
    <p>Preview 1</p>
  </div>
</div>
<style>
  .project-preview {
    width: 100%; height: 50%;
    position: relative;
    overflow: visible;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center; align-items: center; /* alignment for children*/
    background: rgba(var(--black), 0.05);
		box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(var(--black), 5%);
    border-radius: 50px;
  }
  .preview-entry {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-start; align-items: center; /* alignment for children*/
    position: absolute; top: 2; left: 2;
    width: 90%; height: 90%; 
    opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }
  .preview-entry.active { opacity: 1; z-index: 10; }

  .drgmod-btn{
    padding: 0.6em 1.5em;
    border-radius: 9999px;        /* makes it capsule */
    border: none;
    background: rgba(var(--black),0.2);
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .drgmod-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.03);
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 6px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  }
</style>